==Swahili==
===Etymology===
From Arabic {{ARchar|[[رفيق]]}} (''rafí:q'', 'companion,' 'buddy,' 'comrade,' 'partner') < {{ARchar|[[رفق]]}} (''ráfaqa'', 'to be kind,' 'to be friendly, 'to be courteous').

===Noun===
'''rafiki''' (''noun 5/6 plural:'' [[marafiki]]), (''noun 9/10 plural:'' '''rafiki''')

# [[friend|Friend]].
# [[comrade|Comrade]].

